                        "config": {
                            "content": "<h3><strong style=\"background-color: transparent;\">What it doesn't do</strong></h3><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">In the interest of saving you time:</span></p><ul><li><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">The CMS is field-based, not WYSIWYG. It's structured content, not a drag-and-drop editor.</span></li><li><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">No built-in analytics of any kind. You can install any package you like on your site — analytics just isn't what we do here.</span></li><li><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">No tracking cookies. This product doesn't use cookies for any non-functional purpose, and neither does this website.</span></li><li><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">No in-app refunds. Refunds are recorded but issued through Stripe.</span></li></ul>"
